{"tid":2320413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港突現紫荊黨 中共地下黨浮出水面 跟朱鎔基有關？","createTime":"2020-12-10T20:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T21:07:36.000Z","uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"99357e9dbb7ef73c6f5ae197c808d876afdd4f93","tid":2320413,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:24:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">香港突現紫荊黨 中共地下黨浮出水面 跟朱鎔基有關？</span></strong><br />\n楊正2020.12.10 23:18紫荊黨中共管控香港權貴鬥爭朱鎔基<br />\n<br />\n【希望之聲2020年12月10日】（本台記者楊正綜合報導）中共不斷收緊對香港的管控，在此之際，<span class=\"red\">香港突然出現了一個新的政黨&ldquo;紫荊黨&rdquo;，其核心成員都是在中國大陸出生長大。該黨號稱要吸收25萬黨員</span>，外界懷疑中共早已在香港各個角落安插的地下黨員或藉此付出水面。也有分析認爲，該黨的出現或令中共各路權貴鬥爭更加激烈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.soundofhope.org/2020-12/1607613303992.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.soundofhope.org%2F2020-12%2F1607613303992.png&h=690c2d55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.soundofhope.org/post/452332?lang=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F452332%3Flang%3Db5&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=59b47844\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundofhope.org/post/452332?lang=b5</a>"},{"pid":"c3762fe315596adbb6ebb6b7e7932c83f0697250","tid":2320413,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:25:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">紫荊黨起底 紅二代做靠山 <br />\n打北京旗號 投資往績平平</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】<span class=\"red\">近日紫荊黨「橫空出世」，引起政經兩界關注，紫荊黨由全國政協委員李山帶頭，夥同中播控股（471）主席黃秋智、及卓悅控股（653）主席陳健文成立，標榜為「海歸派」金融精英，目標黨員25萬，被指挑戰到建制派地位，引起建制不安。本報追蹤李山人脈，其和國家開發銀行關係最為密切，背後離不開國開行前董事長、非習近平派系的陳元。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/KH3COHGHOVGBNP6HNZT5WSQOZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2FKH3COHGHOVGBNP6HNZT5WSQOZY%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=149b50ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2FKH3COHGHOVGBNP6HNZT5WSQOZY%2F&h=748e726b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/KH3COHGHOVGBNP6HNZT5WSQOZY/</a>"},{"pid":"907ada8d9dbc057c0a98bc9cd740a4563c4f5ecd","tid":2320413,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:27:09.000Z","msg":"幾時有溫家寶？"},{"pid":"ba98d7b7e7887c07d812eba071ebdb6acf2d8148","tid":2320413,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"907ada8d9dbc057c0a98bc9cd740a4563c4f5ecd","tid":2320413,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:27:09.000Z","msg":"幾時有溫家寶？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:30:39.000Z","msg":"等待香港地下黨浮現"},{"pid":"f0916eb0eec3e5494011a270e1bfe8fadb6faf7d","tid":2320413,"uid":231933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:53:19.000Z","msg":"啤梨哥是否黨員？"},{"pid":"61674c4ef16ed743f03640a67df7c7a6ea0b3157","tid":2320413,"uid":290633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:53:44.000Z","msg":"算唔算Deep state<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74106b89e6fee6b6a14e35b5eb5f1d2988e84ea8","tid":2320413,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"61674c4ef16ed743f03640a67df7c7a6ea0b3157","tid":2320413,"uid":290633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:53:44.000Z","msg":"算唔算Deep state<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:55:14.000Z","msg":"super Deep state"},{"pid":"747ccf00907a36f1965fd6daf463f11212b0b9df","tid":2320413,"uid":65770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:56:47.000Z","msg":"#鬥紅"},{"pid":"49b225484f48850a704f7381ba7d7581b2cdaa02","tid":232